[Coös,

December, 1881.] Parsons v. Hilliard & a. James I. Parsons, for the plaintiff. Dudley Sf Remich, W. H. Shurtleff, and Ray, Dreiv Jordan, for the defendants. Carpenter, J.

In an action referred by agreement there is no right of review. Bennett v. Atwood, 57 N. H. 216; Carroll v. Locke, 58 N. H. 163; Rand v. Merchants’ Despatch Co., 60 N. H. 276.

Doe, C. J., did not sit: the others concurred.
